DORA (Reg. EU 2022/2554) — TLPT obbligatorio per soggetti finanziari
ETSI EN 303 645 — 13 requisiti baseline per IoT consumer
IEC 62443 — zone/conduit model per OT/IoT
Radio Equipment Directive 2014/53/UE art. 3.3 — cybersecurity IoT
